{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Last_Happy_Night",
  "title": "The Last Happy Night",
  "summary": "At the Coronet City spaceport on Corellia, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios returns from a day of discreet errands to the ship Uwannabuyim, where her student, the mechanic-apprentice Orson, deep in Force meditation, tinkers obsessively on a prototype lightsaber. Reunited with her beloved Simon, the Selas warrior-mystic, Jessalyn announces she has reserved rooms at a seaside inn for the night. Simon gently cautions Orson that building a weapon of light is a matter of heart and soul rather than mere engineering, and both he and Jessalyn warn the eager apprentice about the dangers of the Dark Side and the need to practice his shielding against the threat of Tazecks. As the lovers prepare to leave, a chill from a troubling vision of the future grips Jessalyn, which she promises to share with Simon later. Orson, sensing the doomed nature of their romance, waves them off to go surfing alone while the two depart for Coronet's golden shore.",
